descriptionHtml:
This is my first boss dungeon mod. In my boss dungeons there are rooms with bosses and good loot.
When you\\\'ve done the first room you can go to the second and so on. The first room is easy and the last is hardest. recommended lvl for this dungeon is 20 or higher. The dungeon is located near riverwood, otherside of the river. If you like the mod please leave a like and comment:D
Thank you.
author: Boss Dungeon
